<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04827</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT REGULATING THE OPERATION OF DRONES OR REMOTELY-PILOTED AIRCRAFT SYSTEMS (RPAS) AND PRESCRIBING PENALTIES FOR VIOLATIONS THEREOF AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : " Drone Regulation Act "</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides that no individual shall operate a drone or RPAS unless he or she has undergone education in safe airspace practices or operating remote-controlled aircraft; States that the the Civil Aviation Authority of the Phils. shall undertake the seminar and issue the necessary certificate of completion with regards to such education.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CASTELO, WINSTON &quot;WINNIE&quot;</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-01-25</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2017-02-01</td></tr></table>